OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises for sharing
OL,4,Cpost about Golders Green police
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski has
OL,8,Fapologised for "sharing a tweet in
OL,9,Fhaste" which accused police officers
OL,10,Fof repeatedly kicking the Golders
OL,11,FGreen stabbing suspect in the head
OL,12,Fafter he had been incapacitated.
OL,14,FPolanski's statement came after Met
OL,15,FPolice commissioner, Mark Rowley,
OL,16,Fwrote to the Green Party leader saying
OL,17,Fthe post had been "inaccurate and
OL,18,Fmisinformed".
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@FO]yD@SOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
