FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777680175
OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises for sharing
OL,4,Cpost about Golders Green police
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FIn a statement on Friday, Polanski
OL,8,Fsaid he had invited Rowley to meet him
OL,9,Fto "discuss the police response and
OL,10,Fthe wider issues raised in his letter."
OL,12,FThe original post on X had accused the
OL,13,Fofficers of "repeatedly and violently
OL,14,Fkicking a mentally ill man in the
OL,15,Fhead" after he was Tasered.
OL,17,FPolanski said: "Everyone in leadership
OL,18,Fhas a responsibility for lowering the
OL,19,Ftemperature at a time of such tension,
OL,20,Fand I apologise for sharing a tweet in
OL,21,Fhaste.
OL,26,@rD@gO]uD@MOUwD@EO]yD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777680175
OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises for sharing
OL,4,Cpost about Golders Green police
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,F"Police responses to emergency
OL,8,Fsituations such as these do need later
OL,9,Freflection in the right forums, but I
OL,10,Faccept that social media is not the
OL,11,Fappropriate channel for doing so."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
