PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777680175
OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises for sharing
OL,4,Cpost about Golders Green police
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FIn a letter to Polanski sent on
OL,8,FThursday, Rowley said his officers
OL,9,F"are nothing short of extraordinary",
OL,10,Fadding: "Without their efforts to stop
OL,11,Fhim, I dread to think what the outcome
OL,12,Fcould have been."
OL,14,FHe continued: "London's Jewish
OL,15,Fcommunities are scared.
OL,17,F"They have experienced a series of
OL,18,Ftargeted attacks on the community, and
OL,19,Fthey expect our officers to act and
OL,20,Fprotect them.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@dO]rD@IOUtD@QO]vD@OOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777680175
OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises for sharing
OL,4,Cpost about Golders Green police
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,F"That is exactly what our officers did
OL,8,Fyesterday. Your decision to criticise
OL,9,Fthese officers, using your public
OL,10,Fprofile and reach, will have a
OL,11,Fchilling effect."
OL,13,FPolanski, who is himself Jewish, and a
OL,14,Fmember of the London Assembly, which
OL,15,Fholds the responsibility for
OL,16,Foverseeing the Met Police, shared a
OL,17,Fsocial media post on X accusing
OL,18,Fofficers of "repeatedly and violently
OL,19,Fkicking a mentally ill man in the head
OL,20,Fwhen he was already incapacitated by a
OL,21,FTaser."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
