OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises for sharing
OL,4,Cpost about Golders Green police
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FThe post was referencing the arrest of
OL,8,Fa man suspected of stabbing two Jewish
OL,9,Fmen in Golders Green.
OL,11,FEssa Suleiman, 45, the alleged Golders
OL,12,FGreen attacker, is accused of trying
OL,13,Fto kill Shloime Rand, 34, and Norman
OL,14,FShine, 76, during a knife rampage
OL,15,Fthrough the streets of the north
OL,16,FLondon suburb on Wednesday.
OL,18,FHe has also been charged with the
OL,19,Fattempted murder of a third man, who
OL,20,Fis alleged to have known him, in south
OL,21,FLondon earlier that day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
