PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777680175
OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises for sharing
OL,4,Cpost about Golders Green police
OL,5,Cofficers
OL,7,FDespite Polanski's apology, a senior
OL,8,FGreen Party source told ITV News:
OL,9,F"There's real concern in the party
OL,10,Fover the sharing of the tweet.
OL,12,F"Some of the leadership's recent
OL,13,Fcomments are clearly antisemitic
OL,15,F"The test now is what action the
OL,16,Fleadership takes around candidates who
OL,17,Fhave made antisemitic remarks
OL,19,F"There are far too many incidents, not
OL,20,Fconsistent action and not swift enough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
